# Git-friendly experiment summaries
# Keep small paper-facing CSV/JSON/Markdown tables under experiments/tables/ trackable.
# Large/raw run artifacts should stay under experiments/outputs/ above.
experiments/tables/**/smoke*/
experiments/tables/**/*smoke*
experiments/tables/**/*.parquet
experiments/tables/**/*.pkl
experiments/tables/**/*.pickle
experiments/tables/**/*.npy
experiments/tables/**/*.npz

